{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/phpcon-2022/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"marcingladkowski.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e33ceae9-7a04-51bd-b579-bc58191c4203","excerpt":"This year conference PHPcon Poland 2022 was so special for me. Everything because I presented a topic\n\"Memory leaks in long processes - practice\". On material I worked with Łukasz Jaworski. For me an…","html":"<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/63217/presentation_1.jpg' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 75.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='presentation_1' title='' src='/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/a22ce/presentation_1.jpg' srcset='/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/0b705/presentation_1.jpg 170w,\n/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/31389/presentation_1.jpg 340w,\n/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/a22ce/presentation_1.jpg 680w,\n/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/29373/presentation_1.jpg 1020w,\n/static/b4d0055fe31a890293612fef3ec4d444/63217/presentation_1.jpg 1024w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>presentation_1</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>This year conference <a href=\"https://2022.phpcon.pl/\">PHPcon Poland 2022</a> was so special for me. Everything because I presented a topic\n\"Memory leaks in long processes - practice\". On material I worked with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/%C5%82ukasz-jaworski-977078130\">Łukasz Jaworski</a>. For me and Łukasz\nit was the first time as presenters. That experience gives me a lot of confidence and bravery. As a programmer\nI always wanted to do something for community by first open source commits and share knowledge, my point\nof see.</p>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/120d2/presentation_2.jpg' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 75.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='presentation_2' title='' src='/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/a22ce/presentation_2.jpg' srcset='/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/0b705/presentation_2.jpg 170w,\n/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/31389/presentation_2.jpg 340w,\n/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/a22ce/presentation_2.jpg 680w,\n/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/29373/presentation_2.jpg 1020w,\n/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/232dc/presentation_2.jpg 1360w,\n/static/f3d23b6d0dee6a15a7dde4b49fab2622/120d2/presentation_2.jpg 4000w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>presentation_2</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Repository with examples: <a href=\"https://github.com/lljaworski/memory_leak_php\">https://github.com/lljaworski/memory_leak_php</a></p>\n<p>Presentation on slides:</p>\n<iframe src=\"https://www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/key/GnjXvRToOdqeIi?hostedIn=slideshare&page=upload\" width=\"476\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n<p>I've got plan to write blog posts about this topic.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"PHPcon Poland 2022","date":"November 15, 2022","update":"November 15, 2022","tags":["conference"],"series":null},"fields":{"slug":"/phpcon-2022/","readingTime":{"minutes":0.51}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"57f2837d-042f-5460-8bb6-fd4495576bc2","fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello world"}}},{"node":{"id":"15d38b46-7f4e-5d99-92b1-18b74982f8d2","fields":{"slug":"/warsawjs-desing-patterns/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"WarsawJs 44 Design patterns"}}},{"node":{"id":"e9bb0690-14f3-5e9f-9328-584c9f24e8c1","fields":{"slug":"/about/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"About"}}},{"node":{"id":"4ad66fcd-90b1-5304-a213-1c3fc30b256b","fields":{"slug":"/bash-training/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Bash training"}}},{"node":{"id":"48928a16-f1c5-5d1b-a33d-0f50d18db0ff","fields":{"slug":"/bash-training-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Bash training 2"}}},{"node":{"id":"3b607386-b659-5272-8fa3-ffa04fb840cb","fields":{"slug":"/summary-2020-plans-for-2021/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Summary 2020 - plans for 2021"}}},{"node":{"id":"6d347c29-ca14-5af3-9aec-3c7e8d0f7a69","fields":{"slug":"/clean-code-workshop/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Clean Code workshop"}}},{"node":{"id":"ef5db6bd-0695-5ada-978e-1ccfd2017d58","fields":{"slug":"/python-crash-course/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Python Crash Course (2nd Edition)"}}},{"node":{"id":"2644cac0-2d10-5868-a75f-137b451040d4","fields":{"slug":"/simple-object-factory/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Simple test object factory"}}},{"node":{"id":"20d57f83-d16f-5fd2-b695-d1aaf2bf4ce2","fields":{"slug":"/where-is-TDD/"},"fro